00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,240
Save him!

7
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,360
Let's go.

8
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,640
Hurry, save him!

9
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,330
Alright!

10
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,530
Let's go!

11
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,740
