12
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,060
Don't let them escape!

13
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,750
Hurry up and leave!

14
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:22,360
Alright!

15
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,329
Let's go.

16
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:37,870
Here.

17
00:03:46,670 --> 00:03:47,740
Miss Huo.

18
